<div class="title">Tip: Bonus item scale</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use more than one event procedure to offer a bonus item scale. This allows you to offer different variations depending on the value of items customers buy. In the first event procedure, e.g. set the item value filter to <strong>&gt;= 100.00 GBP</strong> and <strong>&lt; 200.00 GBP</strong>. In the second event procedure, set an item value filter of <strong>&gt;= 200.00 GBP</strong> and select a different, more attractive variation.</p>
